The paper proposes a state space model based on generative piecewise-linear recurrent neural networks (PLRNN) to assess dynamics from neuroimaging data. This involves the use of machine learning techniques such as neural networks and state space models, which are commonly associated with the computer science sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE), social and information networks (cs.SI), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and computational engineering, finance, and science (cs.CE).
